    ('(?i)\\b(?:session_id|token)\\b.{0,40}\\b(?:sequential|predictable|increment)\\b', 'medium', 'mcp-session-hijacking-no-nonce: Detects MCP server configurations that lack nonce mechanisms or session freshness guarantees.'),
